				<header>
					<h2>How does the rating system work?</h2>
				</header>

							

				<p>You may vote on a coffee shop as many times as you wish.  Did things change since you last rated a coffee shop?  Feel free to update your vote to reflect those changes.  User votes regarding atmosphere, community, and coffee are averaged to give to the “coffee pot rating”.</p>				
				<div class="clearer"></div>
		</article>
